OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,7,Frain feeding in from the west. This
OL,8,Fwill see rain mainly focused in the
OL,9,Fwest with eastern areas staying
OL,10,Flargely dry. Winds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and dull day
OL,13,Fwith outbreaks of rain and drizzle
OL,14,Fthroughout, which may be heavy and
OL,15,Fpersistent at times, particularly in
OL,16,Fthe west. Breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
