OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy Monday and Tuesday with
OL,7,Frain spreading east. Rain mainly in
OL,8,Fthe west with many eastern parts
OL,9,Fseeing largely dry conditions. Drier
OL,10,FWednesday with bright or sunny spells.
